{"tid":123312,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"一個納粹份子走到酒吧","createTime":"2017-02-16T18:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-17T17:10:51.000Z","uid":84615,"like":13,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16fa3bc5821ff2a612ff0bad78105a08b16ebc86","tid":123312,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:12:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">見到有篇文幾得意所以post黎分享下</span></span><br />\nA Nazi goes to a bar<br />\n一個納粹份子走到酒吧 <br />\nA Nazi goes to a bar, looks around, and sees an Orthodox Jew sitting at a nearby table.<br />\n一個納粹份子走到酒吧，在内四處張望，發現鄰近的桌子正有一個正統派猶太人坐著。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Barkeep!&quot;, he says, &quot;A round on me for everyone but that gentleman right there.&quot; <br />\n納粹份子呼叫：「Barkeep！」，並說：「為我替在場所有人準備一回合的飲料，除了那位男士。」<br />\n<br />\nEveryone in the bar receives a cocktail, he looks over at the Jew and notices him smiling back. <br />\n在場所有人都獲得一杯雞尾酒。納粹份子看著那猶太人卻發現猶太人向他展露笑顏。<br />\n<br />\nThe Nazi is not amused, goes back to the bar<br />\n&quot;Barkeep! I want to order a second round for everyone but him, and this time make it all top shelf&quot;.<br />\n那納粹份子感到不快，再次走到櫃臺下單：「Barkeep！我要為在場所有人，除了他，準備另一回合的飲料。這次更要是準備最貴的。」<br />\n<br />\nNazi looks again at the Jew, sees him STILL smiling back.<br />\n納粹份子再望向那猶太人，發現猶太人再次對他露出笑容。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Is that Jew an idiot or what?&quot;<br />\n納粹份子問：「那猶太人是個傻子嗎？」<br />\n<br />\nBartender responds: &quot;Oh no my friend, that's the owner.&quot;<br />\n調酒師回答：「噢，不是呢，我的朋友。那是店主。」"},{"pid":"d5c72cdd221201931280ad75e86e91c549fc09f4","tid":123312,"uid":12518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:16:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ddc890399a7827d1ccba376840aa8aaaa37cc900","tid":123312,"uid":1020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"882ad2356d01285a118ccf36ea371738fb162cd3","tid":123312,"