ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n直接推舊post咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa772b90c56c85f580f69832c79debc2e15e139","tid":123312,"uid":37678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:50:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上面既笑話係源自brettanderson巴打</blockquote><br />\n原post都未沉 你分享黎有咩意義呢<br />\n要分享你直接去推返原本個post作用仲大啦"},{"pid":"8f88de461607d9fd0c373c66482b225240f74fba","tid":123312,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:53:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上面既笑話係源自brettanderson巴打</blockquote><br />\n原post都未沉 你分享黎有咩意義呢<br />\n要分享你直接去推返原本個post作用仲大啦</blockquote><br />\n我今日去講故台揾唔返個Post,而且我唔係唯一一個，為左等眾多未睇過既巴打可以enjoy到咁好笑既笑話，我先開新post分享比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9b9ca56d1f15e7d645fb80a5178001d8b5edfc","tid":123312,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:57:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上面既笑話係源自brettanderson巴打</blockquote><br />\n原post都未沉 你分享黎有咩意義呢<br />\n要分享你直接去推返原本個post作用仲大啦</blockquote><br />\n我今日去講故台揾唔返個Post,而且我唔係唯一一個，為左等眾多未睇過既巴打可以enjoy到咁好笑既笑話，我先開新post分享比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如網絡笑話之類常被人互傳，又習各家之大成的休閒分享，難以每每像引用、轉載人們認真創作的網絡或刊物連載故事、藝術作品等寫下出版日期、出版地、作者等等資訊及考慮法律問題。如果一個論壇、分享專頁等連一點點小分享也容不下，想是有點矯枉過正。"},{"pid":"c4b48bc0b0e6571e29e7a275c748a4e6c9f17271","tid":123312,"uid":12518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T18:57:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac574dfddfe4113d37c3a10ea00d0a1b28593662","tid":123312,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T19:03:05.000Z","msg":"In Soviet Russia, an American spy tries to blend in...<br />\n一個美國間諜嘗試融入蘇聯<br />\n<br />\nGeorge Keats had trained 20 years for this moment. <br />\n佐治基斯為了這個時刻操練了二十年。<br />\n<br />\nHe had mastered the Russian language in its native accent. <br />\nHe learned all of Russia's customs and social graces. He memorized Moscow streetmaps and knew every back-alley there was. He swore that he could even think like a Russian.<br />\n他精通俄文，並有地道口音。他學習了所有的俄國習俗和社交方式。他記下了莫斯科地圖並知道每一條小路的所在地。他發誓他更可以像個俄國人般思考。<br />\n<br />\nThe big day finally came, and he was parachuted to the outskirts of Moscow at night. He emerged by daybreak, and hopped onto a bus going to the city center.<br />\n大日子終於到了。他以跳傘方式在夜間登陸莫斯科的市郊地帶。隨著日出，他打算乘巴士到市中心。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Comrade. How much for a ticket to Red square?&quot;, he asked the conductor in authentic Russian.<br />\n&quot;5 Rubles, Comrade American&quot;, came the reply.<br />\n佐治以天衣無縫的俄文問售票員：「同志。前往Red Square的車票甚麼價錢？」<br />\n售票員說：「五盧布，美國同志。」<br />\n<br />\nKeats was stunned. Perhaps the conductor was just being a smart-ass. He hopped off the bus and asked a passerby for directions to the closest bar.<br />\n基斯受驚，心想希望只是那售票員機靈。他下了巴士後詢問一位路人如何前往最就近的酒吧。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;It's just around the block, Comrade American.&quot;<br />\nKeats' doubts grew immensely. Not knowing what to do, he went inside the bar and ordered a glass of Vodka.<br />\n路人說：「美國的朋友，轉角就是了。」這令基斯心中的疑惑迅速增長。不知所措的他走入酒吧叫了一杯伏特加。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Want some Borscht to go with it, Comrade American?&quot;, the bartender asked.<br />\n調酒師問道：「要些菜湯嗎？美國同志。」<br />\n<br />\nKeats threw a fit. &quot;What's the matter with you people? I dress just like you, I speak just like you, I even THINK just like you! Why does everyone keep calling me American?&quot;<br />\n基斯反應甚大的問道：「你們都怎麼了？我穿和你們一樣的衣服。我跟你們說一樣的話。我甚至像你們一樣思考呢！為何你們總叫我做美國人？」<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Well Comrade, it's because you're black.&quot;<br />\n「是咁的，同志。那是因為你是個黑人。」"},{"pid":"a411f67b6ecf3d4bf2c6c5ec094476a8607b0696","tid":123312,"uid":17516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T20:02:13.000Z","msg":"On9 咁我睇原post 好過啦<br