<br />\n你自己都講左重點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />o</blockquote><br />\n大家都唔係為錢，一人少一句，大家開開心心咪好囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65861d58880ad3640297d295e3a23e5f1cabe9a3","tid":123312,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:39:00.000Z","msg":"A Female Gorilla Is Alone In A Cage At A Zoo<br />\n一隻雌性猩猩孤獨地被困在動物園的籠中<br />\n<br />\n...She has become very cranky due to her isolation and has become increasingly aggressive. <br />\n她因被孤立而變得很暴躁，而且好勇鬥狠。<br />\n<br />\nHer problematic behaviour has become a concern of the zookeeper who decided to try to fix it.<br />\n她那難應付的行為令一個動物管理員很關注，他決定了要解決這問題。<br />\n<br />\nWhile trying to come up with a solution he notices the janitor, a very sleazy redneck type and gets an idea. He walks over to him and asks him a question. <br />\n當管理員嘗試找尋方法的時候，他留意到身邊一個看上去是低劣的鄉下人的守門人，靈機一觸想到一個辦法。他走向守門人問他一個問題。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Would you be willing to... perhaps have sex with a gorilla for 500 dollars?&quot;<br />\n管理員：「不知道......你會否有興趣與一隻猩猩做愛呢？條件是有五百元。」<br />\n<br />\nThe janitor thinks about it for a while and agrees but on 3 conditions. <br />\n守門人想了一會兒後答應了，但有三個要求。<br />\n<br />\n&quot;First, I don't want to have to kiss her,&quot; he says, &quot;second, I don't want anyone to know about this!&quot; <br />\n守門人說：「第一，我不希望要親吻她。第二，我不希望有任何人知道這件事！」<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Alright,&quot; says the zookeeper, &quot;and what's the third condition?&quot;<br />\n管理員：「好的，那第三個要求是甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n&quot;I'm going to need a little bit more time to come up with the 500 dollars.&quot;<br />\n守門人回答：「我需要多一點時間搜集那五百元。」"},{"pid":"432be4fec5c93473b476baf87c298e317c79efe0","tid":123312,"uid":22331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b3997960f976bff67a992b6eff42c7214348848","tid":123312,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T03:48:26.000Z","msg":"What is the difference between E.T. and an illegal immigrant?<br />\nE.T.與非法入境者之間有何分別？<br />\nE.T. learned the language, and eventually went home.<br />\nE.T.學習當地語言，最後回家。<br />\n<br />\nTeacher asks class: &quot; use the word Dandelion in a sentence&quot;<br />\nJamaican student: &quot;the cheetah is faster dandelion.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe Doctor Gave Me 6 Months To Live<br />\n那醫生給了我六個月生存時間<br />\nSo I shot him. The judge gave me 20 years. <br />\n所以我槍殺了他。法官給了我二十年。"},{"pid":"9fbb664dbb363739b14e80eb9c76664110f20ce3","tid":123312,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76afd178eccbdc159aa5515c8d60e3e3f2a0ff6","tid":123312,"uid":11672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:25:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵唔舊post你又copy到d文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n突破盲腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96946fca1e9d0be948873993db78ff85760f559","tid":123312,"uid":84615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>搵唔舊post你又copy到d文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n突破盲腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記憶力好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96edf72db0be590a2ad2bc95b41360ff4d0c5eb","tid":123312,"uid":60365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-17T04:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵唔舊post你又copy到d文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n突破盲腸<img 